# ============================================
# Environment Variables (copy to .env and fill in)
# ============================================
# WHAT: Settings that change between development and production
# WHY:  Never put passwords in code! Store them here.
#       .env is in .gitignore so it NEVER goes to GitHub

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://optimizer:opt_pass@postgres:5432/optimizer_db
SPARK_MASTER=spark://spark-master:7077
```

### 3f) Create `.gitignore`

New File → `.gitignore`:
```
# ============================================
# Files Git should IGNORE (never upload to GitHub)
# ============================================

# Environment variables (contains passwords!)
.env

# Python cache files
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Docker volumes data
data/delta/*
!data/delta/.gitkeep

# IDE settings
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Spark logs
spark-warehouse/
derby.log
metastore_db/